The outer sliding door handle on my bus has a thoroughly mangled lock (I can
see springs and tumblers pointing in all the wrong directions if I look in
the key hole).  Is there a way to  install a new lock into the existing
handle or am I better off looking for a different handle with a key.  Its a
71 btw.

Hal

